{"tid":1880229,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求日文大大翻譯】有日本人為香港示威寫咗兩首詩仲投埋稿登咗上網","createTime":"2020-02-14T16:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T13:06:37.000Z","uid":93310,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"372ece3e26db72bf30d7546ec8388a18ec600669","tid":1880229,"uid":93310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac開post<br />\n<br />\n之前我拜託另一個朋友開的post: [Twitter 文宣] 我係一個6月就有喺Twitter做日文文宣嘅香港人，想比巴絲們一d玩twitter嘅建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我一直都有係twitter做日文文宣，都吸引唔少我的follower關注香港示威。上年12月個時我就有一個follower dm我話想用香港示威寫詩參加日本既寫詩活動：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SgmV6qV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgmV6qV.jpg&h=4ade23b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話見到個活動主題係「光」，就諗起「光復」香港，作咗首詩，問我可唔可以拎黎交上去。我梗係話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYfvVjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYfvVjB.jpg&h=9304f939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢話另一個主題係「冬」，問我有咩建議。我就send咗呢張圖比佢，然後佢又用黎作咗首詩<br />\n<br />\n佢係1月個時交稿，個活動衣家出咗結果，佢兩首詩都比人upload咗上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動網址：<a href=\"http://yomutokaku.jp/result_sp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyomutokaku.jp%2Fresult_sp.html&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=d40a9bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://yomutokaku.jp/result_sp.html</a><br />\n<br />\n佢叫桐島こより，冬個首叫「新年快樂」，光個首叫「光復」，大家碌下就會見到。<br />\n<br />\n光復<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeJNc6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeJNc6w.jpg&h=d118cf0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年快樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/778pZMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F778pZMD.jpg&h=21949d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於佢兩首詩都係base on我同佢既對話，所以佢首詩係圍繞一個女仔（即係我），但佢講既都係成個香港既故事<br />\n<br />\n小妹日文不才，無咁高日文水平將佢兩首詩翻譯做中文，但佢真係寫得好好，希望有日文大大出手翻譯比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多外國人都身體力行支持我地架，希望係呢個艱難既時期比到d力量大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7b067af75c1f2b8f071a8d721a684f1ad0f46f","tid":1880229,"uid":283569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"咁有心！"},{"pid":"0419929fa68db83b89e176f43ae7c4cf9f19584d","tid":1880229,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"可以把全文貼出來方便翻譯"},{"pid":"c0d7d61f2fcda0ee3d0649e7a028639a61b1c00e","tid":1880229,"uid":93310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0419929fa68db83b89e176f43ae7c4cf9f19584d","tid":1880229,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"可以把全文貼出來方便翻譯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年快楽<br />\n<br />\n水面の反射光が眩しく<br />\n思わず復活の呪文を唱えた<br />\n香典すら渡せなかった<br />\n彼女が捨てられた港で<br />\n<br />\n時が止まった彼女を<br />\n千代に八千代に刻むべく<br />\n革の手袋を捨て<br />\n凍えた指で生命線をなぞる<br />\n<br />\n三三五五に消えた仲間からはぐれ<br />\nあどけなさの残る顔で大人に囲まれ<br />\n何一つ訴えることもできず<br />\n救いを求めることもできず<br />\n<br />\n彼女が欠けた世界で<br />\n一人静かに佇む<br />\n不滅の精神を悼む<br />\n可憐な笑顔を憶う<br />\n<br />\n線香を手向ける<br />\n花火の上がらない港で<br />\n爆竹を飾る人々　<br />\n餃子を包む指に痛みを加え<br />\n油の海に涙を添え投げ込む"},{"pid":"e79214b940aff0472238259cd653f45967253f75","tid":1880229,"uid":93310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"另一首<br />\n<br />\n光復<br />\n<br />\nわたしたちの国は<br />\nかつて光を奪った<br />\n土地を　言葉を　誇りを<br />\n多くのひとから奪った<br />\n<br />\n秋の銀座　友は言う<br />\n「半年前は郷里も凪いでいた」<br />\n<br />\n秋の銅鑼湾　友は見る<br />\n催涙弾が飛ぶ　血が流れる<br />\n小さな画面の向こうのにおい<br />\n数日前までの友の世界<br />\n<br />\nわたしはそのにおいを知らない<br />\nわたしはまた奪っている<br />\n　<br />\n訳知り顔で同情を寄せ<br />\n手を握り励まし<br />\nそして彼女の世界を奪う<br />\n<br />\n銀座に催涙弾は撃ち込まれない<br />\n半年後の閃光　流血<br />\nわたしには見えない"},{"pid":"3227ba1415a5865f0709702d05f837b138615c96","tid":1880229,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"Good聽日翻翻，依家上床，早抖"},{"pid":"b6fb59cbbc0e11e4968e8f9cf81885b883f58241","tid":1880229,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"留名睇翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該樓主幫我同佢講聲多謝 <br />\n好感激"},{"pid":"a7d9857594839c1995f9cd069772dab36eb0b7bc","tid":1880229,"uid":93310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3227ba1415a5865f0709702d05f837b138615c96","tid":1880229,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"Good聽日翻翻，依家上床，早抖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />譯完我會send番比我個日本朋友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318d4fb912630cf55f298ed3c2ccad229b7001c1","tid":1880229,"uid":93310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6fb59cbbc0e11e4968e8f9cf81885b883f58241","tid":1880229,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"留名睇翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該樓主幫我同佢講聲多謝 <br />\n好感激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"好 我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b3fb69da72f555958f49a693416168c7a018dc","tid":1880229,"uid":100368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20